'''Lowal Pulse''' was a male [[Human/Legends|Human]] native to [[Metellos/Legends|Metellos]]. He was born a simple groundpounder in one of the countless slums that comprised the majority of the planet's surface, but he eventually made a name for himself in the gladiatorial arenas, both as an expert fighter and as a man who would do anything for the right price. Eventually he began competing in the floating city of [[Ektra]], far above the urban blight. He worked as a ringer for the [[Nonsu]] Corporation, viciously assaulting his opponents and occasionally throwing a fight when ordered to. A quirk of his was to cut a notch in his ear after each victory. When not competing, he wandered the [[Moridebo district|Moridebo District]], spying on his fellow Nonsu employees.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

